data.description: Discover the epitome of rural serenity on this expansive five-acre property with a triple-wide home perched upon a full basement, boasting a walk-out feature that maximizes space and potential. Here, you'll be treated to unobstructed panoramic views of the majestic Pikes Peak, creating a daily backdrop of natural wonder. Car enthusiasts and hobbyists will delight in the large five-car detached garage, a haven for vehicles and recreational equipment. The interior is bathed in natural light thanks to many new Pella windows, while fresh new carpeting adds a cozy touch. The heart of this home is the generously sized kitchen, featuring a U-shaped island tailor-made for entertaining, complemented by three ovens for effortless hosting, and an abundance of cabinets and counter space. The unfinished basement, complete with structural steel support to allow for the open floorplan, invites your creative vision, whether you envision a recreation room, a home gym, or additional living quarters. Beyond the home, the sprawling property invites exploration, from leisurely strolls to enjoying the Colorado nights, all while soaking in the mesmerizing vistas of Pikes Peak. Nestled in a tranquil rural setting, this property offers a peaceful escape, yet remains conveniently close to essential amenities and services. If you're seeking a rural haven with modern comforts and endless potential, schedule a showing today and seize the opportunity to make this picturesque retreat your new home.
